1
00:01:31,100 --> 00:01:35,220
=The Tale of Rose=

2
00:01:35,240 --> 00:01:39,100
=Episode 6=

3
00:01:40,560 --> 00:01:42,790
Every time we argued,

4
00:01:42,790 --> 00:01:44,370
you always nitpicked about words

5
00:01:44,600 --> 00:01:45,610
and made long-winded speeches.

6
00:01:46,390 --> 00:01:47,230
In fact,

7
00:01:47,380 --> 00:01:48,720
you were just trying to cover up

8
00:01:48,720 --> 00:01:50,540
(Contacts Huang Yimei)
your guilt and incompetence.

9
00:01:50,780 --> 00:01:52,020
Once I saw through that,

10
00:01:52,340 --> 00:01:54,380
I lost even the desire
to argue with you.

11
00:01:54,820 --> 00:01:56,540
Does that count as arguing?

12
00:01:57,380 --> 00:01:59,180
We're well-educated.

13
00:01:59,580 --> 00:02:01,780
We should discuss things
calmly and rationally.

14
00:02:02,460 --> 00:02:04,940
Identify problems, analyze problems,
and solve problems.

15
00:02:05,180 --> 00:02:08,140
Using language to resolve conflicts,
isn't that right?

16
00:02:08,660 --> 00:02:10,060
At least I tried.

17
00:02:10,420 --> 00:02:11,460
I have a clear conscience.

18
00:02:11,980 --> 00:02:13,220
But do you have a clear conscience

19
00:02:13,660 --> 00:02:15,340
about the money?

20
00:02:15,340 --> 00:02:17,740
Regarding money, I am ashamed.

21
00:02:18,660 --> 00:02:21,540
But maintaining a family
isn't just about money.

22
00:02:21,540 --> 00:02:22,500
There's also affection.

23
00:02:23,660 --> 00:02:25,100
When you left without a word,

24
00:02:25,380 --> 00:02:26,980
over thousands of miles,

25
00:02:26,980 --> 00:02:28,220
you enjoyed your life,

26
00:02:28,220 --> 00:02:29,900
while I wallowed in self-pity.

27
00:02:30,140 --> 00:02:31,380
There's no debt between us.

28
00:02:32,020 --> 00:02:33,380
I left without a word,

29
00:02:33,860 --> 00:02:34,980
but I was alone in France,

30
00:02:34,990 --> 00:02:36,220
without even knowing the language,

31
00:02:36,220 --> 00:02:37,700
unable to rent a house.

32
00:02:37,700 --> 00:02:39,380
I worked with the locals

33
00:02:39,380 --> 00:02:40,260
but had to put in

34
00:02:40,260 --> 00:02:41,820
ten times the effort they did.

35
00:02:42,060 --> 00:02:42,900
Your clairvoyance

36
00:02:42,940 --> 00:02:44,460
and clairaudience

37
00:02:44,460 --> 00:02:46,060
couldn't see or hear all that.

38
00:02:46,340 --> 00:02:47,740
All you could see

39
00:02:47,740 --> 00:02:49,500
was me dating those men.

40
00:02:50,140 --> 00:02:51,580
Beauty fades quickly.

41
00:02:52,420 --> 00:02:53,820
Fleeting youth.

42
00:02:54,660 --> 00:02:57,700
It's nice to be with someone
when you're alone outside.

43
00:02:59,100 --> 00:03:00,220
Your mother and I

44
00:03:00,220 --> 00:03:02,300
have agreed for a long time.

45
00:03:02,300 --> 00:03:04,660
Our marriage is only in name.

46
00:03:04,660 --> 00:03:06,980
It's not like she cheated on me.

47
00:03:08,900 --> 00:03:09,820
Zhuang Taiwen,

48
00:03:09,820 --> 00:03:10,780
before I went abroad,

49
00:03:10,780 --> 00:03:12,380
I already asked you for a divorce.

50
00:03:12,660 --> 00:03:14,260
It was you who procrastinated.

51
00:03:14,860 --> 00:03:16,940
The headquarters was urging me.
I couldn't wait.

52
00:03:17,300 --> 00:03:20,140
I won't waste my life because of you.

53
00:03:20,980 --> 00:03:22,300
You didn't waste it.

54
00:03:22,300 --> 00:03:24,300
Haven't you been changing boyfriends?

55
00:03:24,300 --> 00:03:25,660
One after another.

56
00:03:25,660 --> 00:03:26,940
You keep getting younger ones.

57
00:03:26,940 --> 00:03:29,180
You even found one as young as your son.

58
00:03:29,180 --> 00:03:30,740
How can you do that?

59
00:03:31,060 --> 00:03:32,740
- None of your business.
- I'm curious.

60
00:03:32,740 --> 00:03:34,540
When you go out with such a boyfriend,

61
00:03:35,100 --> 00:03:36,700
do people wonder

62
00:03:36,700 --> 00:03:38,740
if he's your son or your husband?

63
00:03:39,420 --> 00:03:40,380
Shut up.

64
00:03:57,900 --> 00:03:59,260
Not everyone is like you,

65
00:03:59,260 --> 00:04:00,780
worshiping money.

66
00:04:00,780 --> 00:04:02,180
I have dreams.

67
00:04:02,580 --> 00:04:04,820
I've been writing
continuously for ten years.

68
00:04:04,820 --> 00:04:06,500
I have a new work now.

69
00:04:06,500 --> 00:04:08,420
I'm telling you.

70
00:04:08,420 --> 00:04:10,620
This woman seems to have a lover.

71
00:04:10,620 --> 00:04:12,380
She's getting divorced from her husband.

72
00:04:12,380 --> 00:04:15,660
Is that handsome guy
her lover or her son?

73
00:04:15,660 --> 00:04:17,860
No way, that's too big a difference.

74
00:04:18,540 --> 00:04:19,940
He's really handsome.

75
00:04:20,460 --> 00:04:21,820
If you can't earn real money,

76
00:04:22,020 --> 00:04:24,100
no matter how much poetry you write...

77
00:04:25,980 --> 00:04:26,860
Come in.

78
00:04:27,180 --> 00:04:28,260
You'll hear better inside.

79
00:04:36,620 --> 00:04:37,460
Guodong.

80
00:04:37,860 --> 00:04:40,060
Guodong, I'm not mad at you.

81
00:05:10,580 --> 00:05:16,140
(To Huang Yimei:
Do you have a boyfriend?)

82
00:05:25,060 --> 00:05:27,460
(To Huang Yimei:
When will you come back?)

83
00:05:44,420 --> 00:05:46,860
(From Zhuang Guodong:
When will you come back?)

84
