87
00:06:31,260 --> 00:06:32,580
- Hello.
- Hello.

88
00:06:33,460 --> 00:06:35,420
Didn't expect you to call.

89
00:06:38,580 --> 00:06:39,660
I need to report the situation

90
00:06:39,660 --> 00:06:41,180
