91
00:06:42,100 --> 00:06:43,180
I'm going back on Sunday.

92
00:06:45,660 --> 00:06:46,500
Okay.

93
00:06:46,700 --> 00:06:47,540
Got it.

94
00:06:47,940 --> 00:06:50,140
I won't be on your project team
after I go back.

95
00:06:50,500 --> 00:06:51,500
I've transferred

96
00:06:52,260 --> 00:06:54,020
