97
00:07:03,020 --> 00:07:04,500
Will I still see you then?

98
00:07:20,040 --> 00:07:21,580
♪In the night♪

99
00:07:22,180 --> 00:07:23,020
Hello?

100
00:07:23,290 --> 00:07:24,620
♪Stars above♪

101
00:07:25,260 --> 00:07:26,580
Do you want to ask if the guy

102
00:07:26,580 --> 00:07:28,980
