108
00:07:38,620 --> 00:07:39,460
Right.

109
00:07:40,340 --> 00:07:41,780
He looks like my mom.

110
00:07:42,580 --> 00:07:44,060
I look like my dad.

111
00:07:45,340 --> 00:07:46,740
Then your dad must be very pretty.

112
00:07:47,930 --> 00:07:49,220
