153
00:11:26,820 --> 00:11:28,660
Okay? Focus on this exhibition.

154
00:11:30,420 --> 00:11:32,180
But you're still Tina's assistant,

155
00:11:32,180 --> 00:11:33,740
so don't neglect your main job.

156
00:11:34,020 --> 00:11:34,860
Okay.

157
00:11:34,900 --> 00:11:35,740
Don't forget

158
00:11:35,860 --> 00:11:36,860
to go to the admin office

159
00:11:37,460 --> 00:11:38,620
and print a box of business cards.

160
00:11:51,700 --> 00:11:54,220
Su, you don't have to force topics

161
00:11:54,220 --> 00:11:55,220
to ease the awkwardness.

162
00:11:56,260 --> 00:11:57,580
I didn't hear anything.

163
00:12:00,740 --> 00:12:01,580
Really.

164
00:12:04,100 --> 00:12:04,940
Eat.

165
00:12:47,380 --> 00:12:48,740
It's burning.

166
00:13:02,740 --> 00:13:03,620
This way, this way.

167
00:13:03,980 --> 00:13:04,940
Where are you?

168
00:13:05,180 --> 00:13:07,220
(From Zhuang Guodong:
I'm waiting at the exit.)

169
00:13:07,220 --> 00:13:08,380
What are you doing? Let's go.

170
00:13:10,220 --> 00:13:11,060
I saw you.

171
00:13:12,580 --> 00:13:14,460
I need to go to the bathroom.

172
