188
00:15:21,640 --> 00:15:24,940
♪Sleep peacefully♪

189
00:15:25,270 --> 00:15:30,900
♪Have a sweet dream♪

190
00:15:32,620 --> 00:15:39,610
♪In the dawn after the rain♪

191
00:15:55,340 --> 00:15:57,060
I have to go. It's too late.

192
00:15:57,340 --> 00:15:58,180
Don't go.

193
00:16:01,420 --> 00:16:02,260
Don't go.

194
00:16:53,740 --> 00:16:54,580
You're back.

195
00:16:56,860 --> 00:16:57,900
Where were you so late?

196
00:16:57,900 --> 00:16:58,780
Are you a zombie?

197
00:17:04,780 --> 00:17:05,820
Look at the time.

198
00:17:06,820 --> 00:17:08,020
Look at the time.

199
00:17:08,020 --> 00:17:08,860
What time is it?

200
00:17:08,860 --> 00:17:10,540
I should thank you.

201
00:17:10,540 --> 00:17:11,380
Thank me for what?

202
00:17:12,540 --> 00:17:13,380
Thank...

203
00:17:14,220 --> 00:17:15,820
Thank you for waiting so late for me.

204
00:17:18,180 --> 00:17:19,660
The flight was at 6:30 pm.

205
00:17:19,660 --> 00:17:21,500
Even with traffic,
you should've been home by 9.

206
00:17:21,500 --> 00:17:22,780
Now it's the middle of the night.

207
00:17:22,780 --> 00:17:23,980
I called you, but you didn't answer.

208
00:17:23,980 --> 00:17:25,380
I had to lie to our parents.

209
00:17:26,940 --> 00:17:28,460
I was entertaining the boss.

210
00:17:31,940 --> 00:17:32,980
What?

211
00:17:33,300 --> 00:17:34,940
Why do you smell like men's cologne?

212
00:17:36,540 --> 00:17:37,380
Were you with that guy

213
00:17:37,900 --> 00:17:39,820
in the blue shirt?

214
00:17:42,660 --> 00:17:44,700
I was having dinner with my boss.

215
00:17:44,700 --> 00:17:45,540
Nonsense.

216
00:17:45,940 --> 00:17:47,500
Had dinner right
after your business trip?

217
00:17:47,820 --> 00:17:50,300
I came back just for this dinner.

218
00:17:50,300 --> 00:17:51,220
The flight was delayed.

219
00:17:51,220 --> 00:17:52,240
I dragged my suitcase

220
00:17:52,250 --> 00:17:53,460
and didn't even have time to drop it off.

221
00:17:53,460 --> 00:17:54,380
Is it easy for me?

222
00:17:58,540 --> 00:17:59,700
Was it just you two at the dinner?

223
00:18:00,620 --> 00:18:01,460
Yes.

224
00:18:01,620 --> 00:18:03,100
Just having dinner
with an important client.

225
00:18:03,100 --> 00:18:04,180
I couldn't answer the phone.

226
00:18:04,180 --> 00:18:05,660
What kind of client? Male or female?

227
00:18:09,380 --> 00:18:10,700
Who's texting you so late?

228
00:18:10,700 --> 00:18:12,140
Come on, let me see.

229
00:18:12,780 --> 00:18:14,620
It's probably the boss
asking if I got home.

230
00:18:14,620 --> 00:18:15,980
Then show me.

231
00:18:16,220 --> 00:18:17,580
Show you what?

232
00:18:17,580 --> 00:18:18,980
- I'm worried.
- Go back, go back.

233
00:18:18,980 --> 00:18:19,820
Come on.

234
00:18:19,860 --> 00:18:20,640
Show me.

235
00:18:20,650 --> 00:18:21,900
- If you have nothing to hide,
- Good night.

236
00:18:21,910 --> 00:18:23,510
- why are you afraid to show me?
- Good night, good night.

237
00:18:23,520 --> 00:18:24,180
Let me see.

238
00:18:24,180 --> 00:18:25,020
Who texted you?

239
00:18:34,500 --> 00:18:37,300
(From Zhuang Guodong: I miss you.)

240
00:18:45,140 --> 00:18:47,940
(From Zhuang Guodong: I miss you.)

241
00:18:57,590 --> 00:19:01,720
♪I left you alone♪

242
00:19:02,840 --> 00:19:07,790
♪I know too tight in a road♪

243
00:19:09,760 --> 00:19:18,250
♪Beside, beside a word♪

244
00:19:22,780 --> 00:19:25,480
♪Alone♪

245
00:19:26,100 --> 00:19:27,300
Rosie, have your breakfast.

246
00:19:27,500 --> 00:19:28,420
- Come on.
- I...

247
00:19:29,460 --> 00:19:30,300
Come back.

248
00:19:30,420 --> 00:19:31,260
One.

249
00:19:31,420 --> 00:19:32,580
- Sit down and eat slowly.
- Take more.

250
00:19:32,580 --> 00:19:33,420
Take more.

251
00:19:38,540 --> 00:19:39,380
Dad!

252
00:19:39,540 --> 00:19:41,020
- Bag.
- Rosie.

253
00:19:41,020 --> 00:19:42,220
You forgot your bag.

254
00:19:42,220 --> 00:19:43,060
Here.

255
00:19:43,500 --> 00:19:44,340
Take it.

256
00:19:46,300 --> 00:19:47,180
Alright, I'm leaving.

257
00:19:47,540 --> 00:19:48,780
- Slowly.
- Rosie.

258
00:19:51,860 --> 00:19:52,900
Get in the car. I'll take you.

259
00:19:52,900 --> 00:19:53,900
That's nice of you.

260
00:19:55,180 --> 00:19:56,300
Hurry, hurry, hurry.

261
00:19:56,300 --> 00:19:57,180
There's no time.

262
00:19:58,860 --> 00:20:00,660
Why did you suddenly decide
to take me today?

263
00:20:01,180 --> 00:20:02,140
Running errands, huh?

264
00:20:27,540 --> 00:20:28,740
- Morning.
- Good morning.

265
00:20:29,180 --> 00:20:30,460
Which room is your boss in?

266
00:20:31,100 --> 00:20:32,460
How can I help you?

267
00:20:32,480 --> 00:20:33,860
Zhenhua, what are you doing?
I'm at work.

268
00:20:33,860 --> 00:20:34,700
I'm with her.

269
00:20:34,850 --> 00:20:35,800
I want to see your boss.

270
00:20:35,810 --> 00:20:36,680
- Take me to him.
- No.

271
00:20:36,690 --> 00:20:37,660
What are you doing?

272
00:20:37,660 --> 00:20:38,980
- Stop making a scene, okay?
- I'm not.

273
00:20:38,980 --> 00:20:40,140
I just want to ask him a few questions.

274
00:20:40,140 --> 00:20:41,380
Don't go crazy, okay?

275
00:20:41,380 --> 00:20:42,220
What did I do to you?

276
00:20:42,230 --> 00:20:43,220
Hurry, hurry, take me there.

277
00:20:43,860 --> 00:20:44,700
Why...

278
00:20:45,060 --> 00:20:45,900
Boss.

279
00:20:52,340 --> 00:20:53,740
You are Huang Yimei's boss?

280
00:20:57,340 --> 00:20:58,180
Yes.

281
00:20:58,620 --> 00:21:00,380
I'm Su Gengsheng. And you are?

